::Hevn::
       He continues to fly at a much higher altitude.  When they stop he 
circles overhead and finally takes the time to inspect the other two bots 
with Blackstorm.  He focuses first on Maxima remembering how disturbed she 
had been when he exited the CR tank at the Predacon base.  He then focused 
his attention on Battera.  He had only heard her voice in the Predacon base 
and hadn't taken the time to look at her.  He knew he recognized her from 
somewhere but he couldn't quite place her.

--part1_3e.2f35b2e8.2be9cd21_boundary
